The website states: We are an underground co'op of ex military corps, ex special forces and trained assassins sponsored by the CheChen Mob, we have agents from Russia, Albania, Ukraine, The United States and UK, our agents are located in more than 28 countries across the globe, our agents are masked, and execute an order perfectly, leaving no mistakes, traces or prints.

On the dark web, the group is generally considered to be one of the more viable hitmen-for-hire operations and many people claim to have used its many 'services'. Visiting the website The Black Mob (TBM), using the anonymous Tor browser, you will find a rudimentary layout and the full range of 'services' offered by the group.

The Black Mob - http://j2dbibq43m4fdyry2pltez346mwneqfl7a5dzr2mgsouhp7lox2eu2qd.onion
